Weather App


favorite cities list among the district capitals of Portugal.

add / remove cities from list


- Ask for the current weather conditions of a city:
	
		- temperature
		- pressure
		- precipitation
		- wind
		- humidity

Image caracterizing those conditions - icon

- Ask for forecast of the next day

	- In 3h intervals 


One page 

	- min and max 
		- temperatues
		- wind
		- precipitation
		- humidity


line graph of the temperatue in these hours:

0h00, 3h00, 6h00, 9h00, 12h00,
15h00, 18h00, 21h00






